edu.udel.cis.taschd.gen

Class TableInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.udel.cis.taschd.gen.TableInstance

  • public class TableInstance
extends java.lang.Object
    TableInstance is an object for storing information for a ScoreTable Each store table will store the information of CourseAssistant CourseInstance Section and rows and columns in the ScoreTable By using this table, we can quick access result in ScoreTable for example: ScoreTable will give a final result of indexes. We can obtaining the pairing section and course assistance by using indexes and tableInstance.
